    <title ixia_locid="1">Conref steps: Supplying environment parameters when creating a heat stack</title>
    <shortdesc ixia_locid="2"/>
    <prolog>
        <author ixia_locid="3">Jim Owens</author>
    </prolog>
    <rcbody>
        <ol id="steps_N10021_N1001E_N10001">
            
                <li id="locate-flavor" ixia_locid="5">On the 
                    <b ixia_locid="7">Admin</b>, then 
                    <b ixia_locid="8">System Panel</b>, then
                    <b ixia_locid="9">Flavors</b> page, locate a <b ixia_locid="10">Flavor Name</b> (a resource
                    profile).</li>
                    
                
                <li id="locate-keypair" ixia_locid="12">On the 
                        <b ixia_locid="14">Project</b>, then
                        <b ixia_locid="15">Compute</b>, then
                        <b ixia_locid="16">Access &amp; Security</b>
                     page, locate a <b ixia_locid="17">Keypair
                        Name</b> to provide secure access to the stack.</li>
                
                
                <li id="locate-image" ixia_locid="19">On the 
                        <b ixia_locid="21">Admin</b>, then
                    <b ixia_locid="22">System Panel</b>, then
                        <b ixia_locid="23">Images</b>
                     page, locate an <b ixia_locid="24">Image Name</b>
                    to specify the VM image used by the stack.</li>
                
                
                <li id="locate-tenant" ixia_locid="35">On the 
                    <b ixia_locid="39">Admin</b>, then
                    <b ixia_locid="41">System Panel</b>, then
                    <b ixia_locid="43">Networks</b>
                     page, click the appropriate network <b ixia_locid="31">Name</b> to open the Network Overview page, and then obtain the
                    network <b ixia_locid="45">ID</b>. </li>
                
                
                <li id="locate-user" ixia_locid="36">On the
                    <b ixia_locid="40">Admin</b>, then
                    <b ixia_locid="42">Identity Panel</b>, then
                        <b ixia_locid="44">Users</b>
                     page, locate the <b ixia_locid="46">User Name</b>
                    for the tenant where the VM will be launched.</li>
                
        </ol>
    </rcbody>
